<section id="how-it-works" class="pb-section"><div class="pb-wrap">
<div class="sec-head">
<div class="sec-eyebrow"><span class="pb-en">how it works</span><span class="pb-es">así funciona</span></div>
<h2 class="pb-h2"><span class="pb-en">Three steps. <em>No surprises.</em></span><span class="pb-es">Tres pasos. <em>Sin sorpresas.</em></span></h2>
<p><span class="pb-en">You don't pay until we agree we can help. We don't take members we can't serve.</span><span class="pb-es">No paga hasta que ambos acordemos que podemos ayudar. No aceptamos miembros que no podamos atender.</span></p>
</div>
<div class="how-grid">
<div class="how"><div class="n"><span class="pb-en">Step one</span><span class="pb-es">Paso uno</span></div><h3><span class="pb-en">Tell Catalina what's coming.</span><span class="pb-es">Cuéntale a Catalina qué viene.</span></h3><p><span class="pb-en">Open the chat and tell her: visit, surgery, move, all of it. She maps the scope, pulls in Mike or Santi when it gets real, and tells you straight if we're the wrong fit.</span><span class="pb-es">Abre el chat y cuéntale: visita, cirugía, mudanza, todo junto. Ella arma el alcance, llama a Mike o Santi cuando se pone serio, y te dice sin rodeos si no encajamos.</span></p></div>
<div class="how"><div class="n"><span class="pb-en">Step two</span><span class="pb-es">Paso dos</span></div><h3><span class="pb-en">We build the runway.</span><span class="pb-es">Armamos la pista.</span></h3><p><span class="pb-en">Itinerary, intros, paperwork, providers, staged in the order you'll actually need them. You read; we do.</span><span class="pb-es">Itinerario, contactos, trámites, proveedores, en el orden que de verdad va a necesitar. Usted lee; nosotros hacemos.</span></p></div>
<div class="how"><div class="n"><span class="pb-en">Step three</span><span class="pb-es">Paso tres</span></div><h3><span class="pb-en">We're on call.</span><span class="pb-es">Estamos al pie.</span></h3><p><span class="pb-en">One WhatsApp thread, one number, two people on the line. For the year, the trip, the surgery week.</span><span class="pb-es">Un solo hilo de WhatsApp, un número, dos personas en línea. Para el año, el viaje, o la semana de cirugía.</span></p></div>
</div>
</div></section>

